headline: 3 Reasons Bitcoin Price Failed to Cross $120K Despite Ethereum All-Time High Rally
summary: Bitcoin’s price stalled at around $117,000 on Saturday, Aug 23, with intraday gains capped at just 3%. By contrast, Ethereum (ETH) surged more than 10% to reach a fresh all-time high of $4,900.
